messages.text: Make it aqua colored in the header.

I've implemented the requested change to make the header aqua colored in the AI product page. The specific modification was:

- **Added CSS styling** to set the header background color to `aqua` (hex code #00FFFF)
- Applied this to the primary header element using the class `.header`

The change will give the header a vibrant aqua blue color that should stand out on the page while maintaining good contrast with text content.
